---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About RubyScript</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8">
        RubyScript is a modern programming language that combines the elegance of Ruby
        with the power of modern web technologies.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Why RubyScript?</h2>
      <p>
        RubyScript was created to bridge the gap between traditional Ruby development
        and modern web applications. It brings the joy and simplicity of Ruby syntax
        to the JavaScript ecosystem, allowing developers to write beautiful, maintainable
        code that runs natively in browsers and Node.js environments.
      </p>

      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Ruby-like syntax with modern JavaScript features</li>
        <li>First-class TypeScript support</li>
        <li>Built-in async/await</li>
        <li>Modern package management</li>
        <li>Native ESM support</li>
        <li>Strong type system</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>